# CreatorBrand environment templates
#
# 1) Local development
#    - Copy  client/.env.example  →  client/.env
#    - Copy  server/.env.example  →  server/.env
#    Then run from creatorbrand/:  npm install && npm run dev
#
# 2) Vercel (frontend only)
#    Do not upload a file. In the project: Settings → Environment Variables, add:
#      VITE_API_URL=https://your-api-host.example.com
#      VITE_SOCKET_URL=https://your-api-host.example.com   (optional, if you use sockets)
#    Redeploy after saving. Names must match exactly (VITE_ prefix).
#
# See also: client/.env.example  and  server/.env.example
